      "originalText": "Block Size: (BLOCK_TILE_N, BLOCK_TILE_M)\n\nEach Thread Computes: \nTHREAD_TILE_M x THREAD_TILE_N element in the output tile in C\n\nBlock Threads: \n(BLOCK_TILE_M * BLOCK_TILE_N) / (THREAD_TILE_M x THREAD_TILE_N)\n",
